### Create a new author
POST http://localhost:3000/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chinua Achebe",
  "age": 45,
  "country": "Nigeria"
}

###

### Get all authors
GET http://localhost:3000/authors

###

### Get author by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/authors/1

###

### Update author
PATCH http://localhost:3000/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 46
}

###

### Delete author
DELETE http://localhost:3000/authors/1
